Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy

Process deployment.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAeBpelDeployer Interface for deployers that deploy/undeploy BPEL to the ActiveBPEL engine.
IAeCatalogDeployer Handles deployments to catalog.
IAeDeploymentContainer Top level interface for wrapping of the deployment details.
IAeDeploymentContext Wraps information about a deployment and provides access to its resources.
IAeDeploymentFactory Factory interface for obtaining individual ActiveBpel deployers and validators.
IAeDeploymentHandler Course grained deployment interface.
IAeDeploymentHandlerFactory Factory interface for creating deployment handlers.
IAeDeploymentId Identifies deployment.
IAeDeploymentInfo This interface defines the methods necessary to implement an object that represents the deployment result for a single PDD in a BPR.
IAeDeploymentSource Interface for deploying bpel process to the engine.
IAeDeploymentSummary This interface defines the methods necessary to implement a deployment summary.
IAePddXmlConstants Interface for the pdd xml constants.
IAePdefDeployer Handles the details of deploying/undeploying partner definitions.
IAePolicyMapper Handle the platform specific details of deploying policy for a web service.
IAeServiceDeploymentInfo Models service data for persistence.
IAeWebServicesDeployer Handle the platform specific details of deploying a web service.
IAeWsddConstants Some constants for creating a wsdd deployment document.
 

Class Summary
AeAbstractDeploymentContext Base class for implementing a deployment context.
AeAbstractDeploymentHandler Base class for AeDeploymentHandler impls.
AeAbstractDeploymentProvider Base class for deployment providers
AeBpelDeployer IAeBpelDeployer impl.
AeCatalogDeployer IAeCatalogDeployer impl.
AeCatalogDeploymentLogger Listens for and logs catalog deploment entries.
AeDelegatingWebServiceDeployer WebServiceDeployer that delegates to the target deployer based on the deployment type specified on the container or overridden by endpoint policy
AeDeployConstants Constants related to process deployment
AeDeployerUtil Utility class for creating deployers from config map.
AeDeploymentContainer Deployment container impl.
AeDeploymentContainerFactory Create and configure the IAeDeploymentContainersneeded for bpr deploys and undeploys.
AeDeploymentFactoryImpl Default IAeDeploymentFactory impl.
AeDeploymentHandler Deployes an IAeDeploymentContainer.
AeDeploymentHandlerFactory Factory for creating new deployment handlers.
AeDeploymentId Uniquely identifies a deployment.
AeDeploymentInfo This class represents information about the deployment of a single deployment unit (PDD) within a BPR.
AeDeploymentProvider This class manages the deployment plans defined for BPEL processes.
AeDeploymentSchemas Helper class for loading schemas used for deploying bpel processes to the engine.
AeDeploymentSummary This class contains all information about the deployment of a single BPR file.
AeDeploymentUtil Utility for deploying bpr's from an InputStream
AeExceptionManagementType Enumeration class for exception management types.
AeExceptionManagementUtil Utility class for process exception management.
AeImplementsOperationVisitor Visitor that checks to see if the process provides an IMA for the given plink and operation.
AeMasterPolicyMapper Policy mapper that calls each configured mapper in turn to provide a complete set of Handlers for policy assertions
AeNewDeploymentInfo Wrapper for deployment information, url, metadata, etc.
AePdefDeployer IAePdefDeployer impl.
AeProcessDeployment Manages process deployment information for a BPEL deployment.
AeProcessDeploymentFactory Factory to create a process deployment from a deployment source.
AeProcessPersistenceType Enumeration class for process persistence type.
AeProcessTransactionType Enumeration class for process transaction type.
AeRoutingInfo Simple container for returning the routing information for a request.
AeServiceDeploymentInfo Models service data for persistence.
AeServiceDeploymentUtil Static utilities to determine service info from deployment documents
AeServiceMap Maps service names to their deployment information.
AeUnpackedDeploymentStager Responsible for deploying the bprs to the expanded working dir.
 

Exception Summary
AeDeploymentException Indicates an exception having to do with the deployment of the application.
AeOperationNotImplementedException Exception that indicates that the process exists but it doesn't provide an IMA for the requested operation.
AeServiceNotFoundException Exception for a service that wasn't found
